name: Face Detailer with IP-Adapter & Canny
author: @kosmoskatten
description: A workflow to automatically improve faces in an image using IP-Adapter and Canny ControlNet.

data.label: Face Detail Scale
data.notes:
The image is cropped to the face and scaled to 512x512. This value can scale even more. Best result with value between 1-2.

1 = 512
2 = 1024
